Summary: Light Formation floating just south of saint Augustine, Florida!
divs: Sighting DetailsI just saw this event happen, and I know I'm not the only one to have seen it. I was outside on vaction here in St. Augistine Florida . I was getting ready to go out sea fishing at night when I walked out on the deck and I saw a light formation which was hovering it looked like four green lights and it was hovering from left to right slowly. It must of had been there for about a good 10mins then did a circular motion in the sky then took off and formed into one green light going east. There were about 3 or 4 aircraft in the area that might of saw this also as well as many people might of saw this. It happened around 10:15-10:30pm EST
